snippet.textDisplay:
Ya Mustafa, Ya Mujtaba, show us mercy...
Yours is the hand all the helpless and hopless grasp...
I am a sinner, feeble and helpless, friendless and destitute, 
and you are the only one who cares for me...............
This is how Sufi Muslims see Prophet MUHAMMAD peace be upon him. HE is MERCY for whole universe, regardless of race, caste, ethinicity, religion and colour.
And comments in this thread show that people are experiencing this mercy in thier innerself from this beautiful Naat sung by Atif Aslam.
I pay my respect and love to all Indian brothers and sisters who commented here. From Pakistan. 25 Nov 2017.
